  ('dietitian-moex-00153', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關肝臟代謝功能的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["老化紅血球會釋出粒線體", "膽固醇（cholesterol）可轉變為膽紅素（bilirubin）", "血中葡萄糖轉變為肝醣", "膽鹽分解後，會釋出視黃酸（retinoic acid）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00154', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於纖維囊腫（cystic fibrosis）的敘述，下列何者最適當？', '["氯離子通道功能缺失造成", "使過多水分進入胰管", "導致甲狀腺腫大", "出現皮膚纖維化"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00155', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於產熱效應（thermogenesis）對於代謝率影響的敘述，下列何者最適當？', '["甲狀腺素使腦組織的耗氧與產熱增加，造成代謝率增加", "腎上腺素刺激肝醣與三酸甘油酯的代謝與產熱增加，造成代謝率增加", "飲食會引起產熱與增加代謝率，且以脂肪的效應最大", "低溫環境會引起肌肉發抖，同時降低產熱使代謝率下降，以維持體溫"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00156', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '若發生循環性休克（cardiovascular shock）時，下列敘述何者最適當？', '["交感神經活性增加，因此腎臟入球小動脈收縮，造成腎絲球過濾速率下降", "副交感神經活性增加，因此供應皮膚、消化道及肌肉血管收縮，回心血量增加", "副交感神經活性增加，因此腎臟入球小動脈擴張，造成尿液產生及回心血量增加", "交感神經活性增加，因此血管周邊總阻力下降，造成尿液產生及回心血量下降"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00157', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '醛固酮（aldosterone）促進鈉離子再吸收，主要是作用於腎元的那個部位？', '["近曲小管（proximal tubule）", "亨利氏環下行支（descending limb of the loop of Henle）", "皮質部集尿管（cortical collecting duct）", "亨利氏環上行支（ascending limb of the loop of Henle）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00158', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關排尿控制（contorl of micturition）過程中的敘述，下列何者最不適當？', '["膀胱在充滿（filling）期時，會刺激膀胱牽張受器（stretch receptor），神經訊號回傳位於中 腦（mid brain）排尿反射中樞", "排尿反射中樞可活化副交感神經，並作用於膀胱逼尿肌（detrusor muscle）以產生節律性收縮及 尿道內括約肌放鬆", "膀胱在排尿（micturition）期時，陰部神經（pudendal nerve）會受到抑制，因而導致尿道外括 約肌（external urethra sphincter）的放鬆", "膀胱逼尿肌（detrusor muscle）富含間隙接合（gap junction），以整合此平滑肌的動作"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
